{"tid":1512064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家唔使咁驚以武制暴","createTime":"2019-08-27T17:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T07:40:01.000Z","uid":66828,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4d261bd2e82369bf9d8e4bc006640e2d0318c9","tid":1512064,"uid":66828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"反正而家狗狗平時冇乜野都唔會係街巡<br />\n見到仆街藍絲 黑社會咪大大力還拖 速戰速決<br />\n班狗都唔撚會查架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚閪<br />\n<br />\n但係就最緊要快 打完就閃 擾擾攘攘咁等啲狗黎我地就蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c107c006e5c8ffbab77378833b6c3355571afe0c","tid":1512064,"uid":68628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:38:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e75e127cf843bccd4233a7c63c01dc408a6f0765","tid":1512064,"uid":66828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:40:54.000Z","msg":"推啦<br />\n再唔反抗 公義未來臨已經身先士卒"},{"pid":"efa7af84d8508de64ac46e198e9e7139ee4f549d","tid":1512064,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:47:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f99f3b492acb1f833730b9be879b656cf107b3b","tid":1512064,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:49:12.000Z","msg":"對付唔到狗，就對狗仔狗女<br />\n正如狗對付唔到黑社會，就對學生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae9be9b4afef6977495b9deca6c7136df995bc6","tid":1512064,"uid":251237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:53:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6576bf7eb75bdef6eda13269fb71ca0fab248151","tid":1512064,"uid":207706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:55:21.000Z","msg":"其實報警真係無撚用<br />\n721有版你睇<br />\n仲有機會捅返自己一刀"},{"pid":"ac594e0df6e463bd1d67f85961c4754383ffc2f6","tid":1512064,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-2